{'Location': 'Kempegowda International Airport Road, Down Town Park,Sadahalli Gate,, Devanahalli, Bangalore, India, 562157', 'overall_rating': '8.9', 'Name': 'Bloom  Hotel - Bengaluru Airport', 'reviews': [{'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Wonderful stay‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'The hotel is warm, filled with bright decor and aesthetically pleasing rooms and corners, Staff are warm, cordial and helpful. Room are spacious, clean and well maintained. Would recommend this hotel for anyone looking for a comfortable stay in Bengaluru.'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Suprisingly good‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Was my first time with bloom but would definitely recommend to anyone checking this.  

Super clean  room . Polite and helpful staff. Very well groomed as well. Wont mind a longer stay as well üëçüèª'}, {'Review_Rating': '8.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Nice pkace near just outside the airport ‚Äù', 'Review_Body': "I've stayed for 1 night. The hotel was very nice, the rooms were very clean and in general I enjoyed my stay. I would have like to have a proper coffee at breakfast, and was very surprised that filter coffee is not served and coast 145 R. Also, the service at the reception and breakfast was not great. Didn't do a lot to assist me with an issue I had."}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Great hotel for overnight stay for an early flight out‚Äù', 'Review_Body': "We had an early flight and were also dropping off our kids the previous night at the airport. Instead of doing two trips, we decided to stay near the airport. We picked this and for the price, we were pleasantly surprised by the room and how clean it was.  Got a good night's sleep and hot shower before heading out early in the morning. Would do it again in similar circumstances."}, {'Review_Rating': '9.2', 'Review_Heading': 'A hidden gem ‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Excellent place to stay. Clean and beats any luxury hotels with their excellent housekeeping air conditioning and comfort . The breakfast is far the best . Highly recommended if you are staying near the airport '}, {'Review_Rating': '7.2', 'Review_Heading': 'Not value for the money‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Lill bit expensive'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Nice Stay‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'I regularly stay in this property. Neat & clean property with good staff. Food is good. Very close to KIA Airport '}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Great hotel in a decent budget ‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Excellent hotel in a budget just 15-15 mins away from the airport. '}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Great location for airport‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Really enjoyed stay at bloom near airport. Would definitely consider staying at other bloom locations. Overall really great hotel '}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Awesome place‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'I was initially very sceptical, but changed my perception after spending the night. Very new and clean. Hope they maintain the standards for a long time to come.'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.6', 'Review_Heading': 'Great location near airport ‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Brand new modern facility 10 minutes from airport. Restaurant could offer better food choices.'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Comfy easy stay!‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Great place for a quick stay near the airport. Breakfast is delicious, the Masala Dosa was incredible!'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.6', 'Review_Heading': 'Exceptional‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'I would strongly recommend this hotel for anyone who wants to stay closer to the airport and ignore the city traffic. Accessibility between the hotel and airport is super easy and takes only 5 to 10 min.

The hotel is beautifully maintained and the rooms are super clean. It is all about the hygiene, the comfort, the breakfast and the customer experience that matter when you stay in a hotel and this hotel did an impressive job in all of that. Definitely in par with the luxury chain of hotels if you are looking for the essentials rather than luxury or brand name.'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.6', 'Review_Heading': 'Wowza that yellow is Bright!‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'We booked the bloom hotel to stay in the night before an early flight. Check in was easy, breakfast was tasty, and the staff was very helpful. I unfortunately left some items in the room but they kept it stored until I returned a week later. The rooms are bright and clean and comfortable. Really my only complaint would be the music the play in the hallways is quite loud and very audible inside the rooms; but I guess it adds to the "hip vibe". Overall would recommend.'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Nearest to airport ‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Best stay near airport '}, {'Review_Rating': '9.6', 'Review_Heading': 'Go For It‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Staff, cleanliness, facilities, food, everything was Great. Will definitely suggest . '}], 'price': '2,239', 'img_link': 'https://pix8.agoda.net/hotelImages/35702500/-1/8f5b2088d92c2294b5b04b792a2bb4a9.jpg?ce=0&s=1024x768', 'room_size': '16m¬≤', 'amenities': ['2 single beds', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Toiletries', 'Towels', 'Free Wi-Fi in all rooms!', 'TV [flat screen]', 'Air conditioning', 'Desk', 'Closet', 'Ironing facilities', 'In-room safe box'], 'city': 'Bangalore', 'link': 'https://agoda.com/en-gb/bloom-hotel-bengaluru-airport/hotel/bangalore-in.html?finalPriceView=1&isShowMobileAppPrice=false&cid=1844104&numberOfBedrooms=&familyMode=false&adults=2&children=0&rooms=1&maxRooms=0&checkIn=2023-03-18&isCalendarCallout=false&childAges=&numberOfGuest=0&missingChildAges=false&travellerType=1&showReviewSubmissionEntry=false&currencyCode=INR&isFreeOccSearch=false&isCityHaveAsq=f